'''ViSalus'''是一家[[健康|健康]]保健產品公司。公司主要經營減肥瘦身產品，能量飲料和其他營養保健產品。<ref name="MIH">{{cite web |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2012/07/16/2898417_visalus-marries-biggest-loser.html |title=ViSalus marries ‘Biggest Loser’ with new-age Mary Kay to gain fans |date=July 16, 2012 |author=David J. Neal And Hannah Sampson |publisher=The Miami Herald |accessdate=June 2, 2013}}</ref><ref name="CRU">{{cite web |url=http://www.crunchbase.com/company/visalus-2 |title=ViSalus |date= |author= |publisher=CrunchBase |accessdate=June 2, 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211013444/https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/visalus }}</ref> 總公司位於加利福利亞州洛杉磯市和密歇根州特洛伊市。其母公司為布萊思股份有限公司。<ref name="PRN">{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/visalus-wins-prestigious-silver-telly-award-for-vi-anthem-video-202106101.html |title=ViSalus Wins Prestigious Silver Telly Award for "Vi-Anthem" Video |date= |author= |publisher=PR Newswire |accessdate=June 2, 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211013404/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/visalus-wins-prestigious-silver-telly-award-for-vi-anthem-video-202106101.html }}</ref><ref name="CRU"/> 公司首席營銷官為布雷克·馬倫，首席執行官是萊恩·布萊爾。<ref name="BMM">{{cite web |url=http://www.bmmagazine.co.uk/news/17436/visalus-launches-in-the-united-kingdom/ |title=ViSalus Launches in the United Kingdom |date=April 24, 2013 |author= |publisher=Business Matters |accessdate=June 2, 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211013442/https://bmmagazine.co.uk/news/visalus-launches-in-the-united-kingdom/ }}</ref><ref name="PRN"/>

== 歷史==

美国ViSalus公司於2005年由布雷克·馬倫，萊恩·布萊爾及米阿米恩·尼克·薩尼克拉共同創立。<ref name="MIH"/><ref name="PRN"/> 2008年，布萊思股份有限公司對其發起併購，經增投後控股近75%。<ref name="MIH"/> 2013年，公司擴展至[[英國|英國]]，辦公室位於蓋爾福德。<ref name="BMM"/> 羅斯·西蒙斯任總經理。<ref name="BMM"/>

== 產品==

ViSalus公司以其 “Vi™ 90天挑戰－挑戰客戶健康”系列產品而出名。<ref name="MIH"/><ref name="BMM"/><ref name="CRU"/> ViSalus公司產品涵蓋了NEURO, Vi-Net移動和Vi-Shape營養蛋白飲料等系列。<ref name="CRU"/> 產品在[[美國|美國]]，[[加拿大|加拿大]], 和英國等國家銷售。<ref name="MIH"/><ref name="PRN"/> ViSalus是直銷公司，雇有九萬兩千名員工。<ref name="CRU"/><ref name="MIH"/> 2012年，《邁阿密先驅報》曾有胡克·霍肯和阿方索·里貝羅喜愛ViSalus公司產品的報道。<ref name="MIH"/>

== 獎項及嘉許==

* 2013年，ViSalus公司視頻“VI-Anthem”獲“全球品牌內容推廣大賽”品牌類電視獎。<ref name="PRN"/>
* 2010年，美國直銷新聞雜誌授予首席執行官萊恩·布萊爾DSN全球週轉獎。<ref name="FOR">{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/danschawbel/2011/08/08/entrepreneurship-nothing-to-lose-and-everything-to-gain/ |title=Entrepreneurship: Nothing to Lose and Everything to Gain |date=August 8, 2011 |author=Dan Schawbel |publisher=Forbes |accessdate=June 2, 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023525/https://www.forbes.com/sites/danschawbel/2011/08/08/entrepreneurship-nothing-to-lose-and-everything-to-gain/ }}</ref>
	
